   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The liturgist charged with the farming of taxes to the thiefcatcher of the village Karanis. Send up Atisis, son of Akialis (for Akiaris), accused by the tax collector of the village Philopator, either him or 160 drachmas (160dr.)</ab>
